This is my first playthrough Nord at level 40.

Specializes in: 
One-Handed with a focus on Axes
Destruction Magic
Heavy Armor
Enchanting
Smithing

Main Quest has been done up to after the Thalmor Embassy.
Companions Quests have been done and character has been redeemed from Lycanthropy.
College of Winterhold Quests have been done up to after becoming the Arch-Mage.
Is neither alleged with the Stormcloak Rebellion or the Imperial Legion.

Owns Breezehome in Whiterun filled with a lot of loot ... and a Dog :)

The distinctiveness about this character though is that he resembles the glorious
Techno Viking.
